fields.name: Buffalo pizza
fields.description: Delicious twist on the classic pizza, combining the bold flavors of Buffalo chicken wings with the comforting essence of pizza.

fields.name: Cheese pizza
fields.description: Classic favorite that celebrates simplicity and flavor. This delightful dish features a perfectly baked crust topped with a rich, savory tomato sauce and a generous layer of melted mozzarella cheese.

fields.name: Coca-cola
fields.description: Distinct flavor is a carefully guarded secret, combining sweet notes with hints of vanilla, caramel, and a slight acidity that gives it a crisp finish.

fields.name: Salad
fields.description: A refreshing and vibrant Classic Garden Salad is the perfect combination of crisp, fresh vegetables that delight the senses.

fields.name: Dr Peper
fields.description: Unique and iconic soft drink that stands out with its distinctive flavor profile, blending 23 different flavors into a refreshing, fizzy beverage.

fields.name: Dr Peper (diet)
fields.description: Refreshing, calorie-free version of the beloved classic soft drink, offering the same unique blend of 23 flavors that fans have come to love.

fields.name: Frees
fields.description: Fries are a beloved snack and side dish, known for their crispy exterior and fluffy interior.

fields.name: Margarita
fields.description: Each bite delivers a satisfying combination of savory cheese and eggs with a hint of spice, making it a go-to choice for pizza lovers everywhere.

fields.name: Mashed potato
fields.description: Creamy Mashed Potatoes are a timeless comfort food that embodies warmth and indulgence. Made from fluffy, starchy potatoes, this dish is prepared by boiling and then mashing the potatoes to achieve a smooth, velvety texture.

fields.name: Peperoni
fields.description: A classic favorite, Pepperoni Pizza is known for its simple yet bold flavors. It features a crispy, golden crust topped with a layer of tangy tomato sauce, melted mozzarella cheese, and slices of spicy, smoky pepperoni.

fields.description: A zesty blend of spices and fresh veggies, this pizza brings the heat with jalape√±os and chipotle.

fields.name: Veg pizza
fields.description: Plant-based twist on the classic pizza, loaded with fresh and colorful vegetables.

fields.name: Evian
fields.description: Natural mineral water sourced from several springs near Lake Geneva in the French Alps.
